extends helpers/layout

block head
	title Customization to Inactive

block content

	tr(style="background-color: #ffc641;")
		td(valign='top', colspan='2')
			p(style='margin: 48px 0 48px 0; padding:0 50px; font-size: 38px; line-height: 36px; font-weight:bold; text-align:center;')
				| What’s new

	+spacer( 32 )

	tr(style=backgroundColor, width="100%")
		td(valign='top', colspan='2')
			p(style='margin: 0 0 8px 0; padding:0 50px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;')
				| Hi Aviator,
			p(style='margin: 0 0 8px 0; padding:0 50px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;')
				| We miss you and we want you back!
			p(style='margin: 0 0 8px 0; padding:0 50px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;')
				| These last few weeks, we’ve been jammin’ on a series of highly requested updates to help you keep up with your phone and customize your Aviate experience.

	tr(style=backgroundColor, width="100%")
		td(valign='top', colspan='2')
			p(style='margin: 16px 0 8px 0; padding:0 50px; font-size: 22px; line-height: 24px; font-weight:bold;')
				| Icon Packs
			p(style='margin: 0 0 8px 0; padding:0 50px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;')
				| Customize the look and style of your homescreen to make it feel like “home.” We currently support icon packs built for ADW, Apex and Nova launchers. <a style="color:black;" href="http://blog.getaviate.com/post/78699964205/customize-your-homescreen-with-icon-packs" title="Customize Your homescreen with icon packs">Learn More</a>

	tr(style=backgroundColor, width="100%")
		td(valign='top', colspan='2')
			p(style='margin: 16px 0 8px 0; padding:0 50px; font-size: 22px; line-height: 24px; font-weight:bold;')
				| Notification Badges
			p(style='margin: 0 0 8px 0; padding:0 50px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;')
				| See the number of missed or unread communications you have on the messaging/SMS and phone apps you use most. <a style="color:black;" href="http://blog.getaviate.com/post/80708690224/notification-badges-for-aviate-have-landed" title="Notification Badges for Aviate have landed">Learn More</a>

	tr(style=backgroundColor, width="100%")
		td(valign='top', colspan='2')
			p(style='margin: 16px 0 8px 0; padding:0 50px; font-size: 22px; line-height: 24px; font-weight:bold;')
				| Shortcuts
			p(style='margin: 0 0 8px 0; padding:0 50px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;')
				| Get one-tap access to your most important contacts, documents, playlists, or websites. Create your own shortcuts and move them to specific collections, spaces, or favorites for easy access. <a style="color:black;" href="http://blog.getaviate.com/post/77397780485/get-around-faster-with-shortcuts" title="Get around faster with shortcuts">Learn More</a>
			
	tr(style=backgroundColor, width="100%")
		td(valign='top', align="center", colspan='2')
			img(align='center', width='100%', src='http://aviate-website.s3-website-us-east-1.amazonaws.com/mailing-images/customization-features.jpg', alt="Watch Aviate in action here", style='width:100%; margin:24px 0 0;  text-align:center;' )

	+separator( 8 )

	tr(style=backgroundColor, width="100%")
		td(valign='top', align="center", colspan='2')
			a( href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tul.aviate", title="Reinstall Aviate", style="display:inline-block; margin:32px 0 8px; padding:20px 40px; background:#ff5736; border-bottom:5px solid #b0361e; font-size:20px; color:white; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; text-decoration:none;") Update Aviate
			p(style='margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; text-align:center;')
				| If needed, use the code below
			div( href="#", title="Reinstall Aviate", style="display:inline-block; margin:16px 0; padding:20px 40px; background:#d5d5d5;  font-size:20px; color:black; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; text-decoration:none;") 
				| 4V14T3


	tr(style=backgroundColor, width="100%")
		td(valign='top', colspan='2')
			p(style='padding: 10px 0 0 0; margin-bottom:0; text-align:center;')
				| See you soon!
			p(style='padding:0px 0 20px 0; margin-top:0; text-align:center;')
				| Mark, Paul and Will (and the Aviate Team)